org.matsim.contrib.dvrp.tracker

Class TaskTrackers

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.dvrp.tracker.TaskTrackers

  • public class TaskTrackers
extends Object
    General assumptions:
    • An offline tracker knows/uses only the corresponding task and the schedule (i.e. plan)
    • An online tracker knows/uses also the corresponding DynAction (i.e. execution)
